outputs.output_descr: The Programme will assist with national and international expertise the rapid development of capacities to help address the challenges of the transition, which include among others, developing political institutions and responsive leadership for the new political entity, strengthening cohesion among the Bangsamoro, facilitating reconciliation and the development of transitional justice and human rights mechanisms, and strengthening governance within the parameters of the FAB and relevant national frameworks.

project_title: Support to Framework Agreement on Bangsamoro (FAB)
